# Cursor project rules — see CLAUDE.md for full context.

This is a Cloudflare Workers + Remix Shopify app scaffolded by AppApprove.
Blueprint: FAQ.

Conventions:
- Polaris React + App Bridge React, no raw HTML/CSS
- Every admin route uses <Page> with title + primaryAction
- Currency stored as integer cents
- Drizzle migrations need a meta/_journal.json entry for every new SQL file
- No Vite ?raw imports for SQL/text — inline as TS const strings

Forbidden:
- Modifying deploy.yml structure or wrangler.toml schema
- Replacing AppApprove scaffold/auth helpers (extend them instead)
- Breaking pnpm tsc + pnpm test (both must stay green for deploy)

See CLAUDE.md for architecture, domain model, iteration cookbook, and BYOK env vars.
